data.description: Charming colonial style home on over 1/2 acre private lot in a no HOA community! There is plenty of parking on the driveway or in the 2-car garage. You will find a large family room with fireplace & hardwood floors on main level. Kitchen boasts stone countertops, tile floors, stainless steel appliances, and laundry hook-up if you choose! Breakfast area right next to kitchen and separate Large dining room has coffered ceiling. Upstairs has the master suite complete with dual vanity, walk-in tile shower! Split bedroom plan upstairs gives you 2 other secondary bedrooms. Bathrooms have been updated with new vanities and tile throughout! Basement level is finished with large great room, bonus room, bedroom, laundry, and finished bathroom. Don't forget the entertaining space on the oversized rear porch! Roof is 3 years young, Water heater is 1 year young! Fresh paint! There are so many options with this home! This home is conveniently located approx. 1 mile from Pleasant Hill Rd. & Ronald Reagan Pkwy with easy access to I-85 or GA 124!
